      }
    },
    "Vitrine will load this webpage locally in WebKit on your Mac and turn it into an image. The page is rendered on-device — Vitrine never sends the URL to a remote screenshot service." : {
      "comment" : "URL capture first-use disclosure body explaining local WebKit rendering (CS-043).",
      "localizations" : {
        "es" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Vitrine cargará esta página web localmente en WebKit en tu Mac y la convertirá en una imagen. La página se procesa en el dispositivo: Vitrine nunca envía la URL a un servicio remoto de capturas."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Wait until" : {
      "comment" : "Input pane picker label: which signal a web capture waits for before snapshotting.",
      "localizations" : {
        "es" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Esperar a"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Waits a fixed time after the page loads before snapshotting, so content added by scripts has time to appear." : {
      "comment" : "Input pane footer for the fixed-delay wait strategy.",
      "localizations" : {
        "es" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Espera un tiempo fijo después de que la página carga antes de capturar, para que el contenido añadido por scripts tenga tiempo de aparecer."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Waits, up to the chosen time, for the page to stop loading content before snapshotting. Best effort: a page that never goes quiet is captured when the time runs out." : {
      "comment" : "Input pane footer for the best-effort network-quiet wait strategy.",
      "localizations" : {
